{"title":"Small Hands Rejoice, Paul Components Adds New Short Reach Canti Levers","link":"https://bikerumor.com/paul-components-short-reach-canti-levers/","date":1741627431000,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Paul-Comp-Short-Reach-Canti-Levers-hero.webp\" width=\"1280\" height=\"924\" alt=\"(Photos / Paul Component Engineering)\" /></p>\n<p>Here’s a little bit o’ news from Chico, California! The crew at <a href=\"https://www.paulcomp.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Paul Components</a> has just announced new Canti Lever <a href=\"https://www.paulcomp.com/shop/components/brake-levers/short-pull/canti-lever/\" target=\"_blank\">brake levers</a> where the lever blades are designed to sit closer to the bar. This allows riders with a shorter reach to feel comfy with a brake lever made just for them.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Paul-Comp-Short-Reach-Canti-Levers-glamor-shot.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Paul-Comp-Short-Reach-Canti-Levers-glamor-shot.webp\" alt=\"Paul Comp Short Reach Canti Levers glamor shot\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Paul-Comp-Short-Reach-Canti-Levers-glamor-shot.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Paul-Comp-Short-Reach-Canti-Levers-glamor-shot-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Paul-Comp-Short-Reach-Canti-Levers-glamor-shot-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Paul-Comp-Short-Reach-Canti-Levers-glamor-shot-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Paul-Comp-Short-Reach-Canti-Levers-glamor-shot-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Paul-Comp-Short-Reach-Canti-Levers-glamor-shot-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a><figcaption>(Photos / Paul Component Engineering)</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>These new levers for smaller hands will use the same dual-sealed-cartridge bearing and CNC-machined design as the current, best-selling Canti Levers we’ve all come to love. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>They’ll still be offering as “Standard Reach” Canti Levers, so this will just be an additional configuration if you need it. They’re available now directly on the Paul Components website or from your favorite LBS!</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Paul-Comp-Short-Reach-Canti-Levers-first-pic.webp\"><img width=\"1024\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Paul-Comp-Short-Reach-Canti-Levers-first-pic.webp\" alt=\"Paul Comp Short Reach Canti Levers first pic\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Paul-Comp-Short-Reach-Canti-Levers-first-pic.webp 1024w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Paul-Comp-Short-Reach-Canti-Levers-first-pic-240x300.webp 240w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Paul-Comp-Short-Reach-Canti-Levers-first-pic-96x120.webp 96w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Paul-Comp-Short-Reach-Canti-Levers-first-pic-768x960.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Paul-Comp-Short-Reach-Canti-Levers-on-bars.webp\"><img width=\"1024\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Paul-Comp-Short-Reach-Canti-Levers-on-bars.webp\" alt=\"Paul Comp Short Reach Canti Levers on bars\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Paul-Comp-Short-Reach-Canti-Levers-on-bars.webp 1024w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Paul-Comp-Short-Reach-Canti-Levers-on-bars-240x300.webp 240w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Paul-Comp-Short-Reach-Canti-Levers-on-bars-96x120.webp 96w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Paul-Comp-Short-Reach-Canti-Levers-on-bars-768x960.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Paul-Comp-Short-Reach-Canti-Levers-blue-prints.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Paul-Comp-Short-Reach-Canti-Levers-blue-prints.webp\" alt=\"Paul Comp Short Reach Canti Levers blue prints\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Paul-Comp-Short-Reach-Canti-Levers-blue-prints.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Paul-Comp-Short-Reach-Canti-Levers-blue-prints-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Paul-Comp-Short-Reach-Canti-Levers-blue-prints-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Paul-Comp-Short-Reach-Canti-Levers-blue-prints-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Paul-Comp-Short-Reach-Canti-Levers-blue-prints-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Paul-Comp-Short-Reach-Canti-Levers-blue-prints-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2>Canti Lever Retail &amp; Tech Info</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Retail: $209 (pair), $108 (right or left)</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Material: 6061 Aluminum</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Weight: 134g Pair</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Anodized Colors: Black, Purple, Silver, or Pewter</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Cable Pull: Short-Pull</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Machined by us in sunny Chico, California</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Paul-Comp-Short-Reach-Canti-Levers-black.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"960\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Paul-Comp-Short-Reach-Canti-Levers-black.webp\" alt=\"Paul Comp Short Reach Canti Levers black\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Paul-Comp-Short-Reach-Canti-Levers-black.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Paul-Comp-Short-Reach-Canti-Levers-black-297x223.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Paul-Comp-Short-Reach-Canti-Levers-black-120x90.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Paul-Comp-Short-Reach-Canti-Levers-black-768x576.webp 768w\" /></a><figcaption>Black</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Paul-Comp-Short-Reach-Canti-Levers-pewterjpeg.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"960\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Paul-Comp-Short-Reach-Canti-Levers-pewterjpeg.webp\" alt=\"Paul Comp Short Reach Canti Levers pewterjpeg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Paul-Comp-Short-Reach-Canti-Levers-pewterjpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Paul-Comp-Short-Reach-Canti-Levers-pewterjpeg-297x223.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Paul-Comp-Short-Reach-Canti-Levers-pewterjpeg-120x90.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Paul-Comp-Short-Reach-Canti-Levers-pewterjpeg-768x576.webp 768w\" /></a><figcaption>Pewter</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Paul-Comp-Short-Reach-Canti-Levers-purple.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"960\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Paul-Comp-Short-Reach-Canti-Levers-purple.webp\" alt=\"Paul Comp Short Reach Canti Levers purple\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Paul-Comp-Short-Reach-Canti-Levers-purple.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Paul-Comp-Short-Reach-Canti-Levers-purple-297x223.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Paul-Comp-Short-Reach-Canti-Levers-purple-120x90.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Paul-Comp-Short-Reach-Canti-Levers-purple-768x576.webp 768w\" /></a><figcaption>Purple</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Paul-Comp-Short-Reach-Canti-Levers-silver.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"960\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Paul-Comp-Short-Reach-Canti-Levers-silver.webp\" alt=\"Paul Comp Short Reach Canti Levers silver\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Paul-Comp-Short-Reach-Canti-Levers-silver.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Paul-Comp-Short-Reach-Canti-Levers-silver-297x223.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Paul-Comp-Short-Reach-Canti-Levers-silver-120x90.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Paul-Comp-Short-Reach-Canti-Levers-silver-768x576.webp 768w\" /></a><figcaption>Silver</figcaption></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://www.paulcomp.com/\" target=\"_blank\">PaulComp.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/paul-components-short-reach-canti-levers/\">Small Hands Rejoice, Paul Components Adds New Short Reach Canti Levers</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Ron Frazelle","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"78ea733902260792471b3cd15b42bb2252cdd809a08a5937bb5b0ee2ea28e8a8","category":"Cycling"}